                "app_version": "2.9.2",
                "chart": "airflow",
                "first_deployed": 1779555093,
                "last_deployed": 1779555093,
                "name": "airflow",
                "namespace": "data-platform",
                "notes": "\n\n\nThank you for installing Apache Airflow 2.9.2!\n\nYour release is named airflow.\nYou can now access your dashboard(s) by executing the following command(s) and visiting the corresponding port at localhost in your browser:\n\nAirflow Webserver:     kubectl port-forward svc/airflow-webserver 8080:8080 --namespace data-platform\nDefault Webserver (Airflow UI) Login credentials:\n    username: admin\n    password: admin\n\nYou can get Fernet Key value by running the following:\n\n    echo Fernet Key: $(kubectl get secret --namespace data-platform airflow-fernet-key -o jsonpath=\"{.data.fernet-key}\" | base64 --decode)\n\n###########################################################\n#  WARNING: You should set a static webserver secret key  #\n###########################################################\n\nYou are using a dynamically generated webserver secret key, which can lead to\nunnecessary restarts of your Airflow components.\n\nInformation on how to set a static webserver secret key can be found here:\nhttps://airflow.apache.org/docs/helm-chart/stable/production-guide.html#webserver-secret-key\n",
                "revision": 1,
                "values": "{\"config\":{\"core\":{\"load_examples\":\"False\"},\"webserver\":{\"expose_config\":\"True\"}},\"dags\":{\"gitSync\":{\"branch\":\"main\",\"enabled\":true,\"repo\":\"https://github.com/jaymztheking/sports-data-platform.git\",\"subPath\":\"dags\",\"wait\":60}},\"data\":{\"metadataConnection\":{\"db\":\"airflow\",\"host\":\"postgresql\",\"pass\":\"(sensitive value)\",\"port\":5432,\"sslmode\":\"disable\",\"user\":\"postgres\"}},\"env\":[{\"name\":\"AIRFLOW_CONN_SPARK_DEFAULT\",\"value\":\"spark://spark-master:7077\"},{\"name\":\"AIRFLOW_CONN_MINIO_DEFAULT\",\"value\":\"aws://minioadmin:minioadmin@?endpoint_url=http://minio:9000\"}],\"executor\":\"LocalExecutor\",\"fernetKey\":\"(sensitive value)\",\"images\":{\"airflow\":{\"repository\":\"apache/airflow\",\"tag\":\"2.9.3-python3.11\"}},\"migrationJob\":{\"useHelmHooks\":false},\"postgresql\":{\"enabled\":false},\"scheduler\":{\"resources\":{\"limits\":{\"memory\":\"512Mi\"},\"requests\":{\"cpu\":\"100m\",\"memory\":\"256Mi\"}}},\"webserver\":{\"resources\":{\"limits\":{\"memory\":\"512Mi\"},\"requests\":{\"cpu\":\"100m\",\"memory\":\"256Mi\"}},\"service\":{\"ports\":[{\"name\":\"airflow-ui\",\"nodePort\":30007,\"port\":8080,\"targetPort\":\"airflow-ui\"}],\"type\":\"NodePort\"}}}",
                "version": "1.14.0"
              }
            ],
            "name": "airflow",
